_:Nad3037e0bbac48a2a2703e9b23a7d9e4 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Charlotte is an Investment Banker and experienced FTSE Chair and Non-Executive Director. Her long board-level experience spans a host of sectors and industries and covers IPOs, M&amp;A and restructuring. She is a recognised international authority and professor in corporate governance and leadership, and author of Effective Directors, Questions to Ask.</p>\n" .
